---

### 2. `.gitignore`
It is essential to ignore compiled files and IDE settings so your repo stays clean.

```gitignore
# Compiled class files
*.class

# Mobile Tools for Java (J2ME)
.mtj.tmp/

# Package Files #
*.war
*.ear
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.rar

# IDE Specific (IntelliJ)
.idea/
*.iml
out/

# IDE Specific (Eclipse)
.settings/
.project
.classpath
bin/

# Log files
*.log

# Operating System Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db